name: RhinoGATOR
overview:
RhinoGATOR is a job search tool.

RhinoGATOR technology takes the best Open Source Software (OSS) standards, throws in some ANSI standards like EDI (electronic data interchange), and reshapes them to specifically address the marketplace, and synthesize all job feedsâ€”regardless the native format or locationâ€”into a single jobs database for our clients.
